## 1. Minimum playbooks (baseline)
- Disable account (IdP)
- Reset MFA / revoke sessions
- Isolate endpoint (EDR)
- Block IOC (FW/Proxy/DNS)
- Rotate secret (vault)

## 2. Guardrails (mandatory)
- Entry conditions (signal + severity + confidence).
- Reversible actions where feasible.
- Dry-run required in test.
- Stop conditions (false positive handling).

## 3. Approvals
- Baseline: human approval for destructive actions.
- Regulated: two-person rule for critical actions.

## 4. Evidence
- Execution logs + linked IR ticket.
